{"questionId":"27029","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Ammonia, NH<sub>3</sub>, is industrially important for the manufacture of fertilizers, explosives and plastics.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Ammonia is produced by the Haber–Bosch process which involves the equilibrium:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">N<sub>2 </sub>(g) + 3 H<sub>2 </sub>(g)&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" class=\"wrs_chemistry\"><mo>⇌</mo></math> 2 NH<sub>3 </sub>(g)</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Deduce the expression for the equilibrium constant, <em>K</em><sub>c</sub>, for this equation.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>c</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><mrow><mi>N</mi><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><msub><mi>N</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfenced><msup><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfenced><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac></math>&nbsp;✔</p>","meta":{"questionId":"27029","referenceCode":"22M.2.sl.TZ1.2c(i)","subjectId":"45-dp-chemistry-last-assessment-2024","title":"Deduce the expression for the equilibrium constant, Kc, for this equation.","paper":"2","level":"SL","questionNumber":"c(i)","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Core","Core","Topic 7: Equilibrium","7.1 Equilibrium","Core","Topic 7: Equilibrium"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}